highlights.text: “Jhoome Jo Pathaan” by Vishal-Shekhar, Arijit Singh, Sukriti Kakar, Vishal Dadlani, Shekhar Ravjiani, and Kumaar is the highest new entry on Top Songs Bengaluru at #64.
“Jehda Nasha (From "An Action Hero")” by Tanishk Bagchi, Faridkot, Yohani, Amar Jalal, and Harjot Kaur is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Bengaluru, up 46 spots at #45.
Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Bengaluru. “Kesariya” is the highest at #3.
“Tu Aake Dekhle” by King has been on Top Songs Bengaluru the longest, at 63 weeks straight.
